{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01CcXeGN2x9Mg1Dz2oFveCHF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a full picture. Let me design the signatures.\n\nBased on the codebase:\n- **Framework**: Spring Boot + Java\n- **Pattern**: `ResultDTO<T>` responses, layered architecture (Controller → Service → Repo)\n- **Existing bulk flow**: `markAllForReprocess()` + `publishEvent(PolicyReprocessRequestedEvent)` → job picks up INIT entities\n- **Single-entity primitives already exist**: `updateReprocessStateById(Long, ReprocessState)` and `claimInitEntityForReprocess(Long)`\n\n---\n\n## 设计方案\n\n### Controller — `EntityController.java`\n\n```java\n@PostMapping(\"/{id}/reprocess\")\npublic ResultDTO<Void> reprocessEntity(@PathVariable Long id) {\n    entityService.reprocessById(id);\n    return ResultDTO.success(null);\n}\n```\n\n- 无 request body（entityId 已在 path 中）\n- 复用现有 `ResultDTO<Void>` 模式（同 `markAllForReprocess` 无实质返回数据时的惯例）\n- 异常（entity not found 等）由 Service 抛出，由全局 ExceptionHandler 统一处理\n\n---\n\n### Service Interface — `EntityService.java`\n\n```java\nvoid reprocessById(Long id);\n```\n\n---\n\n### Service Impl — `EntityServiceImpl.java`\n\n```java\n@Override\npublic void reprocessById(Long id) {\n    // 1. 验证 entity 存在（不存在则抛 EntityNotFoundException）\n    EntityProcessLockInfo lockInfo = findProcessLockInfoById(id)\n        .orElseThrow(() -> new EntityNotFoundException(id));\n\n    // 2. 若当前已是 RUNNING，拒绝（避免打断正在进行的处理）\n    if (lockInfo.getReprocessState() == ReprocessState.RUNNING) {\n        throw new EntityReprocessConflictException(id, ReprocessState.RUNNING);\n    }\n\n    // 3. 标记为 INIT（幂等：已是 INIT 也可覆盖）\n    updateReprocessStateById(id, ReprocessState.INIT);\n\n    // 4. 触发 job 扫描（复用现有事件机制）\n    eventPublisher.publishEvent(new PolicyReprocessRequestedEvent(1, \"api-single\"));\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 关键设计决策\n\n| 决策点 | 选择 | 理由 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| RUNNING 时拒绝 | 是 | `claimInitEntityForReprocess` 做原子 INIT→RUNNING，若强制覆盖为 INIT 可能造成双重处理竞态 |\n| 复用现有事件机制 | 是 | `PolicyReprocessRequestedEvent` → `PolicyReprocessJob` 路径已有限流、分布式锁、重试，不需另起新路径 |\n| response body | `Void` | 单个 entity 触发是 fire-and-forget，实际结果异步产生，通过 `/entities/{id}/display-status` 轮询 |\n| `triggerSource` | `\"api-single\"` | 与现有 `\"api\"`（批量）区分，便于 metrics 分析 |\n\n---\n\n**需要新增的异常类**（如项目没有）：\n- `EntityNotFoundException` — 404 语义\n- `EntityReprocessConflictException` — 409 语义（RUNNING 冲突）\n\n确认这个设计方向后，我可以直接写实现代码。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4043,"cache_read_input_tokens":17673,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4043},"output_tokens":27,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"96f50260-dc60-4a75-a501-57c5af917508","uuid":"700e1ff5-911d-4efa-afa5-b3e93fb1154c"}
